  "description": "Grains at minimum size — dust. Position scatter at maximum — each grain fires into a random position in the source. Pitch scatter at 0.7 so the grains arrive at different pitches with no musical relationship. Speed is 0, reversed. This is not musical granular synthesis. This is granular violence.",
